div.p:
Jehovah said: "Wherefore, no man can behold all my works, except he behold all my glory;
and no man can behold all my glory, and afterwards remain in the flesh on the earth"
(Moses 1:5).

"And worlds without number have I created; and I also created them for mine own purpose;
and by the Son created them, which is mine Only Begotten Son"
(Moses 1:33).
